{"tid":1010345,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有睇女演員夜凪景","createTime":"2019-02-06T02:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T10:44:14.000Z","uid":7307,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"214a5afbaa36c5d81d909e0b632f545bb110b801","tid":1010345,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T02:39:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c0fmQ73.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc0fmQ73.png&h=940dfd3f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RfD7MGq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRfD7MGq.png&h=c32917b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bJR1Q77.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbJR1Q77.png&h=68684a89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n套野開頭都係普通，不過千世子出場之後去到依家舞台劇篇 ，真係愈來愈好睇<br />\n<br />\n其實最欣賞佢講演員講到不幸既元素，又唔會好似玻璃面具同累咁狗血<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DUoPfA2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDUoPfA2.png&h=94135960&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"538542fd8541b129ab76389c48695b1f395cbaf1","tid":1010345,"uid":25367,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T05:13:33.000Z","msg":"咩叫狗血，你返支那喇"},{"pid":"c4ed71f46a5db5f114203ef9872b4f57d1dca2a1","tid":1010345,"uid":134174,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"538542fd8541b129ab76389c48695b1f395cbaf1","tid":1010345,"uid":25367,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T05:13:33.000Z","msg":"咩叫狗血，你返支那喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T05:19:52.000Z","msg":"狗血關支那咩事<br />\n真心想問"},{"pid":"bf5937bf8424b5a9a0e72ef59eaf2dc437d92316","tid":1010345,"uid":4618,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T20:04:24.000Z","msg":"今日開咗嚟睇，睇到39話<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申:千景派</span></span><br />\n同埋search咗下介紹演技理論簡史嘅文章了解下<br />\n「演技」、再現表演的訓練以及相關理論問題<br />\n<a href=\"http://art.cssn.cn/ysx/ysx_ysx/201805/t20180514_4247870.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fart.cssn.cn%2Fysx%2Fysx_ysx%2F201805%2Ft20180514_4247870.shtml&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTPCGrV5sAEOTHy2vWGvapoA%3D&h=4cd0b256\" target=\"_blank\">http://art.cssn.cn/ysx/ysx_ysx/201805/t20180514_4247870.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n夜凪景課題係如何學習方法演技<br />\n重視即興表演同情感記憶<br />\n呢樣真係無咩新鮮感<br />\n就算到death island篇我都覺得麻麻<br />\n到舞台劇篇先至好睇<br />\n<br />\n千世子理論建基於哥格蘭式表現派<br />\n理性主義至上，無論如何要保持自我冷靜<br />\n呢篇就好似批判緊一個過時理論咁<br />\n史氏流派講發現同建立自我，非理性自我出現係預期結局<br />\n<br />\n同埋商業電影呢種設定我都唔太buy<br />\n世俗化遇到質疑就太易動搖<br />\n表達唔到真正學院嗰種「專業」<br />\n<br />\n舞台劇篇講方法派同體驗派嘅分歧就幾好<br />\n角色塑造係共同終極目標但方法各異<br />\n由自我發展角色同代入角色嘅內外矛盾<br />\n之後再講如何面對死亡<br />\n期待之後點講兩種典型派系分別用咩態度去面對"},{"pid":"bec546c6007709833d4a5b490e649eb13b59e1bf","tid":1010345,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T10:10:50.000Z","msg":"累個表現力高d 次次去到劇台劇位都好投入到 好似比佢吸左入去咁 會好集中精神咁睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb1a440ab2caacebfffbcbb494d7891383084b7","tid":1010345,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bec546c6007709833d4a5b490e649eb13b59e1bf","tid":1010345,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T10:10:50.000Z","msg":"累個表現力高d 次次去到劇台劇位都好投入到 好似比佢吸左入去咁 會好集中精神咁睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T10:37:03.000Z","msg":"不過佢舞台外的野太累<br />\nd真假老母"},{"pid":"0f12c92e3f1837f6592210d11024580e3ce135b1","tid":1010345,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efb1a440ab2caacebfffbcbb494d7891383084b7","tid":1010345,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bec546c6007709833d4a5b490e649eb13b59e1bf","tid":1010345,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T10:10:50.000Z","msg":"累個表現力高d 次次去到劇台劇位都好投入到 好似比佢吸左入去咁 會好集中精神咁睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"re